{"timestamp":"2026-02-10T01:59:00.551Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"call_TQ7MYn5lsbKbAguV4eG3G6AN","output":"Chunk ID: 190f42\nWall time: 0.0504 seconds\nProcess exited with code 0\nOriginal token count: 679\nOutput:\n# Acceptance Test Suite ‚Äî UC-01 View Public Announcements\n\n## Overview\n**Use Case:** UC-01 View Public Announcements  \n**Primary Actor:** Public User (Guest)  \n**Objective:** Verify guests can view public announcements without authentication and that all alternative paths behave correctly.\n\n---\n\n## Assumptions / Test Data\n- Supported browsers: Chrome, Firefox (latest stable).\n- Base URL: `https://<cms-host>/`\n- Announcements are stored in the CMS database and exposed through the announcements page/section.\n- An ‚ÄúAnnouncements‚Äù link exists on the homepage or main navigation.\n\n### Seed Data Sets\n**DS-01 (Normal announcements set)**\n- A1: Title \"Registration Opens\", Body present, Published date present\n- A2: Title \"Keynote Speaker Announced\", Body present, Published date present\n- A3: Title \"Submission Deadline\", Body present, Published date present\n\n**DS-02 (No announcements set)**\n- No announcement records exist.\n\n---\n\n## UC-01-AT-01 ‚Äî Guest can access homepage without login\n**Priority:** P0  \n**Preconditions:** CMS deployed and reachable.  \n**Steps:**\n1. Open the CMS base URL in a supported browser.\n**Expected Results:**\n- Homepage loads successfully (HTTP 200).\n- No login prompt is required to view the homepage.\n- Navigation includes an ‚ÄúAnnouncements‚Äù option.\n\n---\n\n## UC-01-AT-02 ‚Äî Guest can view announcements list (Main Success Path)\n**Priority:** P0  \n**Test Data:** DS-01  \n**Preconditions:** Announcements exist in DB; guest is not logged in.  \n**Steps:**\n1. Navigate to the homepage.\n2. Click ‚ÄúAnnouncements‚Äù in the navigation.\n**Expected Results:**\n- Announcements page loads successfully.\n- Announcements are displayed in a readable format (e.g., list/cards).\n- Each displayed announcement includes at minimum:\n  - Title\n  - Body/summary content\n  - Published date/time (if defined by system)\n- No authentication wall or redirect to login occurs.\n\n---\n\n## UC-01-AT-03 ‚Äî Direct URL access to announcements works for guests\n**Priority:** P1  \n**Test Data:** DS-01  \n**Preconditions:** Announcements page has a direct route (e.g., `/announcements`).  \n**Steps:**\n1. Enter the announcements URL directly in the address bar.\n**Expected Results:**\n- Announcements page loads and displays public announcements.\n- No authentication required.\n\n---\n\n## UC-01-AT-04 ‚Äî Announcements are retrieved from the database successfully\n**Priority:** P1  \n**Test Data:** DS-01  \n**Preconditions:** DS-01 is in the database.  \n**Steps:**\n1. Navigate to Announcements page.\n2. Compare displayed announcement count/titles to DS-01.\n**Expected Results:**\n- All seeded announcements appear.\n- Titles match the stored records.\n- No duplicate or missing announcements relative to DS-01.\n\n"}}
