t tasks use ‚ÄúReviewer‚Äù in phase titles and file names. | Normalize tasks and filenames to ‚Äúreferee‚Äù or note explicit mapping. |\n| F2 | Inconsistency | MEDIUM | plan.md:L24 vs tasks.md | Plan states ‚Äúsingle (server‚Äërendered web app + API)‚Äù, but tasks presume both API and web handlers for every story, including admin/internal flows without UI intent. | Align on UI scope per story or adjust tasks to API‚Äëonly where appropriate. |\n| U1 | Underspecification | MEDIUM | spec.md ¬ßSecurity & Privacy Considerations | Logging exclusions are listed, but data retention and backup expectations (constitution) are not specified in spec/tasks. | Add explicit retention/backup requirements and tasks. |\n| U2 | Underspecification | MEDIUM | spec.md ¬ßUser Acceptance Tests | UAT index location specified, but tasks only create a placeholder and do not require actual indexing from TC‚ÄëXX. | Add concrete task to populate UAT index with TC‚ÄëXX IDs/titles. |\n| E3 | Coverage Gap | MEDIUM | spec.md ¬ßDependencies | Spec depends on UC/TC files as sources of truth; no task validates their presence/consistency. | Add a validation task to ensure UC/TC inventory completeness. |\n| A2 | Ambiguity | MEDIUM | spec.md ¬ßUser Story 5 | ‚Äúvalid, complete, secure registration info‚Äù is undefined. | Specify field rules and validation criteria. |\n| A3 | Ambiguity | MEDIUM | spec.md ¬ßUser Story 23 | ‚Äúefficient and conflict‚Äëfree schedule‚Äù lacks measurable constraints. | Define scheduling constraints and conflict rules. |\n\n### Coverage Summary Table\n\n| Requirement Key | Has Task? | Task IDs | Notes |\n|-----------------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| view-public-announcements | Yes | T019‚ÄìT024 | Mapped to US1 |\n| view-conference-registration-prices | Yes | T025‚ÄìT030 | Mapped to US2 |\n| view-conference-schedule | Yes | T031‚ÄìT036, T187‚ÄìT192 | Duplicate requirement in FR-003 and FR-029 |\n| register-user-account | Yes | T037‚ÄìT042 | Mapped to US4 |\n| validate-registration-information | Yes | T043‚ÄìT048 | Mapped to US5 |\n| log-in-to-system | Yes | T049‚ÄìT054 | Mapped to US6 |\n| change-password | Yes | T055‚ÄìT060 | Mapped to US7 |\n| submit-paper-manuscript | Yes | T061‚ÄìT066 | Mapped to US8 |\n| upload-manuscript-file | Yes | T067‚ÄìT072 | Mapped to US9 |\n| save-submission-progress | Yes | T073‚ÄìT078 | Mapped to US10 |\n| receive-paper-decision | Yes | T079‚ÄìT084 | Mapped to US11 |\n| receive-presentation-schedule | Yes | T085‚ÄìT090 | Mapped to US12 |\n| receive-review-invitation | Yes | T091‚ÄìT096 | Mapped to US13 |\n| accept-or-reject-review-invitation | Yes | T097‚ÄìT102 | Mapped to US14 |\n| access-assigned-papers | Yes | T103‚ÄìT108 | Mapped to US15 |\n| submit-paper-review | Yes | T109‚ÄìT114 | Mapped to US16 |\n| enforce-reviewer-workload-limit | Yes | T115‚ÄìT120 | Mapped to US17 |\n| assign-referees-to-submitted-papers | Yes | T121‚ÄìT126 | Mapped to US18 |\n| ensure-three-reviewers-per-paper | Yes | T127‚ÄìT132 | Mapped to US19 |\n| receive-completed-review-forms | Yes | T133‚ÄìT138 | Mapped to US20 |\n| make-final-paper-decision | Yes | T139‚ÄìT144 | Mapped to US21 |\n| edit-conference-schedule | Yes | T145‚ÄìT150 | Mapped to US22 |\n| generate-conference-schedule | Yes | T151‚ÄìT156 | Mapped to US23 |\n| modify-generated-conference-schedule | Yes | T157‚ÄìT162 | Mapped to US24 |\n| publish-final-conference-schedule | Yes | T163‚ÄìT168 | Mapped to US25 |\n| register-for-conference | Yes | T169‚ÄìT174 | Mapped to US26 |\n| pay-conference-registration-fee | Yes | T175‚ÄìT180 | Mapped to US27 |\n| receive-payment-confirmation-ticket | Yes | T181‚ÄìT186 | Mapped to US28 |\n| view-conference-schedule (duplicate) | Yes | T187‚ÄìT192 | Duplicate mapping for UC‚Äë29 |\n\n**Constitution Alignment Issues**\n- CRITICAL: Missing explicit test tasks for P1/critical flows (constitution ¬ßIII).\n- CRITICAL: Missing explicit audit logging tasks for critical actions (constitution ¬ßIV).\n\n**Unmapped Tasks**\n- 24 tasks