ation','Review','review_access'),\\n (21,'UC-21 Make Final Paper Decision','P1','The decision for each paper is recorded and communicated to the author','Decision','decision_record'),\\n (22,'UC-22 Edit Conference Schedule','P2','The conference schedule is successfully updated and stored, with conflicts resolved and constraints satisfied','Schedule','schedule_edit'),\\n (23,'UC-23 Generate Conference Schedule','P2','A valid conference schedule is generated, stored, and made available for review and further editing','Schedule','schedule_generate'),\\n (24,'UC-24 Modify Generated Conference Schedule','P2','The conference schedule is successfully modified, validated, and stored, reflecting real-world constraints','Schedule','schedule_modify'),\\n (25,'UC-25 Publish Final Conference Schedule','P2','The final conference schedule is published and accessible, and authors and attendees are notified','Schedule','schedule_publish'),\\n (26,'UC-26 Register for Conference','P1','The attendee is successfully registered for the conference and proceeds to payment or confirmation','ConferenceRegistration','conference_register'),\\n (27,'UC-27 Pay Conference Registration Fee','P1','The registration fee is successfully paid, and the attendee‚Äôs participation is confirmed','Payment','registration_payment'),\\n (28,'UC-28 Receive Payment Confirmation Ticket','P2','The attendee receives a payment confirmation ticket that can be viewed or saved as proof of registration','ConfirmationTicket','payment_confirmation'),\\n (29,'UC-29 View Conference Schedule','P3','The attendee successfully views the published conference schedule','Schedule','schedule_view_attendee'),\\n]\\n\\np1_set={4,6,8,9,10,16,18,21,26,27}\\n# critical actions for audit logging by US number\\naudit_us={6,8,9,10,16,18,21,22,23,24,25,26,27}\\n\\ntid=1\\nlines=[]\\nlines.append('---')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('description: \\\"Task list template for feature implementation\\\"')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('---')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append(f'# Tasks: {feature_name}')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('**Input**: Design documents from `/specs/001-uc-spec-union/`')\\nlines.append('**Prerequisites**: plan.md (required), spec.md (required for user stories), research.md, data-model.md, contracts/')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('**Tests**: The examples below include test tasks. Tests are OPTIONAL - only include them if explicitly requested in the feature specification.')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('**Organization**: Tasks are grouped by user story to enable independent implementation and testing of each story.')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('## Format: `[ID] [P?] [Story] Description`')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('- **[P]**: Can run in parallel (different files, no dependencies)')\\nlines.append('- **[Story]**: Which user story this task belongs to (e.g., US1, US2, US3)')\\nlines.append('- Include exact file paths in descriptions')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('## Path Conventions')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('- **Single project**: `src/`, `tests/` at repository root')\\nlines.append('- **Web app**: `backend/src/`, `frontend/src/`')\\nlines.append('- **Mobile**: `api/src/`, `ios/src/` or `android/src/`')\\nlines.append('- Paths shown below assume single project - adjust based on plan.md structure')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('## Phase 1: Setup (Shared Infrastructure)')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('**Purpose**: Project initialization and basic structure')\\nlines.append('')\\nsetup_tasks=[\\n 'Create project structure per implementation plan in src/ and tests/',\\n 'Initialize Python project and dependency manifest in pyproject.toml',\\n 'Configure linting and formatting in pyproject.toml',\\n 'Create base FastAPI app scaffold in src/api/app.py',\\n 'Create web UI scaffold in src/web/app.py',\\n 'Add environment configuration loader in src/config/settings.py',\\n]\\nfor t in setup_tasks:\\n    lines.append(f'- [ ] T{tid:03d} {t}')\\n    tid+=1\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('---')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('## Phase 2: Foundational (Blocking Prerequisites)')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('**Purpose**: Core infrastructure that MUST be complete before ANY user story can be implemented')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('**‚öÝÔ∏è CRITICAL**: No user story work can begin until this phase is complete')\\nlines.append('')\\nfoundational=[\\n 'Setup database connection and base ORM models in src/models/base.py',\\n 'Create Alembic migration setup in alembic.ini and migrations/',\\n '[P] Implement role-based access control middleware in src/api/middleware/rbac.py',\\n '[P] Implement authentication service in src/services/auth_service.py',\\n '[P] Implement audit logging utilities in src/services/audit_log.py',\\n '[P] Implement file storage client in src/services/storage_client.py',\\n '[P] Implement notification service (email) in src/services/notification_service.py',\\n '[P] Implement payment provider client in src/services/payment_client.py',\\n '[P] Implement scheduling engine base in src/services/scheduling_engine.py',\\n 'Create shared API routing in src/api/routes.py',\\n 'Create shared web routing in src/web/routes.py',\\n 'Define UAT index placeholder in specs/001-uc-spec-union/uat/uat-index.md',\\n]\\nfor t in foundational:\\n    lines.append(f'- [ ] T{tid:03d} {t}')\\n    tid+=1\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('**Checkpoint**: Foundation ready - user story implementation can now begin in parallel')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('---')\\n\\nfor num,title,priority,ind_test,entity,slug in stories:\\n    lines.append('')\\n    lines.append(f'## Phase {num+2}: User Story {num} - {title} (Priority: {priority})')\\n    lines.append('')\\n    lines.append('**Goal**: ' + title.split(' - ',1)[-1])\\n    lines.append('')\\n    lines.append('**Independent Test**: ' + ind_test)\\n    lines.append('')\\n    us=f'US{num}'\\n    if num in p1_set:\\n        lines.append(f'### Tests for User Story {num} (REQUIRED for P1) ‚öÝÔ∏è')\\n        lines.append('')\\n        lines.append(f'- [ ] T{tid:03d} [P] [{us}] Create contract test in tests/contract/test_{slug}.py')\\n        tid+=1\\n        lines.append(f'- [ ] T{tid:03d} [P] [{us}] Create integration test in tests/integration/test_{slug}.py')\\n        tid+=1\\n        lines.append('')\\n    lines.append('### Implementation for User Story ' + str(num))\\n    lines.append('')\\n    model_file=f'src/models/{entity.lower()}.py'\\n    service_file=f'src/services/{slug}_service.py'\\n    api_file=f'src/api/{slug}.py'\\n    web_file=f'src/web/{slug}.py'\\n    route_api='src/api/routes.py'\\n    route_web='src/web/routes.py'\\n    tasks=[\\n        f'[P] [{us}] Create or update {entity} model in {model_file}',\\n        f'[P] [{us}] Implement {slug} service in {service_file}',\\n        f'[{us}] Implement API handler in {api_file}',\\n        f'[{us}] Wire API route in {route_api}',\\n        f'[{us}] Implement web handler/page in {web_file}',\\n        f'[{us}] Wire web route in {route_web}',\\n    ]\\n    for t in tasks:\\n        lines.append(f'- [ ] T{tid:03d} {t}')\\n        tid+=1\\n    if num in audit_us:\\n        lines.append(f'- [ ] T{tid:03d} [{us}] Add audit logging for {slug} actions in src/services/audit_log.py')\\n        tid+=1\\n    lines.append('')\\n    lines.append('**Checkpoint**: User Story ' + str(num) + ' should be fully functional and testable independently')\\n    lines.append('')\\n    lines.append('---')\\n\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('## Phase N: Polish & Cross-Cutting Concerns')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('**Purpose**: Improvements that affect multiple user stories')\\nlines.append('')\\npolish=[\\n 'Documentation updates in docs/ and specs/001-uc-spec-union/quickstart.md',\\n 'Code cleanup and refactoring in src/',\\n 'Performance optimization across all stories in src/services/',\\n 'Security hardening review in src/services/auth_service.py',\\n 'Finalize UAT index content in specs/001-uc-spec-union/uat/uat-index.md',\\n 'Run quickstart validation steps in specs/001-uc-spec-union/quickstart.md',\\n]\\nfor t in polish:\\n    lines.append(f'- [ ] T{tid:03d} {t}')\\n    tid+=1\\n\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('---')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('## Dependencies & Execution Order')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('### Phase Dependencies')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('- **Setup (Phase 1)**: No dependencies - can start immediately')\\nlines.append('- **Foundational (Phase 2)**: Depends on Setup completion - BLOCKS all user stories')\\nlines.append('- **User Stories (Phase 3+)**: All depend on Foundational phase completion')\\nlines.append('  - User stories can then proceed in parallel (if staffed)')\\nlines.append('  - Or sequentially in priority order (P1 ‚Üí P2 ‚Üí P3)')\\nlines.append('- **Polish (Final Phase)**: Depends on all desired user stories being complete')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('### User Story Dependencies')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('- **P1 Stories**: US4, US6, US8, US9, US10, US16, US18, US21, US26, US27')\\nlines.append('- **P2 Stories**: US5, US7, US11, US12, US13, US14, US15, US17, US19, US20, US22, US23, US24, US25, US28')\\nlines.append('- **P3 Stories**: US1, US2, US3, US29')\\nlines.append('- P2 stories depend on P1 foundations where applicable (auth, submissions, reviews, payments)')\\nlines.append('- P3 stories can be delivered after foundational setup, independent of P1 business workflows')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('### Parallel Opportunities')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('- All Setup tasks marked [P] can run in parallel')\\nlines.append('- All Foundational tasks marked [P] can run in parallel (within Phase 2)')\\nlines.append('- Once Foundational phase completes, user stories can run in parallel per story')\\nlines.append('- Within each story, model and service tasks marked [P] can run in parallel')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('---')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('## Parallel Example: User Story 1')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('```bash')\\nlines.append('Task: \\\"Create or update Announcement model in src/models/announcement.py\\\"')\\nlines.append('Task: \\\"Implement announcements service in src/services/announcements_service.py\\\"')\\nlines.append('```\\n')\\nlines.append('---')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('## Implementation Strategy')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('### MVP First (User Story 1 Only)')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('1. Complete Phase 1: Setup')\\nlines.append('2. Complete Phase 2: Foundational (CRITICAL - blocks all stories)')\\nlines.append('3. Complete Phase 3: User Story 1')\\nlines.append('4. **STOP and VALIDATE**: Test User Story 1 independently')\\nlines.append('5. Deploy/demo if ready')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('### Incremental Delivery')\\nlines.append('')\\nlines.append('1. Complete Setup + Foundational ‚Üí Foundation ready')\\nlines.append('2. Add User Story 1 ‚Üí Test independently ‚Üí Deploy/Demo (MVP!)')\\nlines.append('3. Add P1 user stories in priority order ‚Üí Test independently')\\nlines.append('4. Add P2 user stories ‚Üí Test independently')\\nlines.append('5. Add P3 user stories ‚Üí Test independently')\\n\\nwith open(tasks_path,'w') as f:\\n    f.write('\\\\n'.join(lines).rstrip()+\\\"\\\\n\\\")\\n\\nprint('tasks_written', tid-1)\\nPY\"}","call_id":"call_m38gHuAyrWguoAdFcVu3umaW"}}
